{"id":150494,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/默克尔纠正其备受争议的言论/","date":"2011-05-07T11:00:23Z","modified":"2011-05-07T11:00:23Z","title":"默克尔纠正其备受争议的言论","content":"<div>\n<p>帕绍<br />德国总理默克尔对其就本拉登死亡发表的备受争议的言论进行了纠正。本周六默克尔对《帕绍新报》记者说， “本拉登是国际恐怖主义组织的头目，他授意实施了巨大的犯罪活动。我们不能因为他无法再给人类制造苦难而掉以轻心。”本拉登被美国特种部队击毙之后，默克尔在一次新闻发布会上表示，她为成功消灭本拉登感到高兴。为此，汉堡一位法官对默克尔总理提起诉讼，指控她公开赞同杀人行为。汉堡检察院称，公开赞同刑事犯罪有可能被判处罚款或者最多3年有期徒刑。</p>\n<p> </p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15057631%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E5%B0%94%E7%BA%A0%E6%AD%A3%E5%85%B6%E5%A4%87%E5%8F%97%E4%BA%89%E8%AE%AE%E7%9A%84%E8%A8%80%E8%AE%BA\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}